<i>noun</i>: 백일몽 [배길몽] <i>verb</i>: 몽상하다 [몽ː상하다] <br>
<ul style="list-style-type:square">
<li><i>noun</i><br>
<dt>백일몽 [배길몽]</dt><br>
<dd>daydream; reverie</dd><br>
<dd>실현될 수 없는 헛된 생각.</dd><br>
<dd>A useless idea that cannot be achieved.</dd><br>
</li>
<li><i>verb</i><br>
<dt>몽상하다 [몽ː상하다]</dt><br>
<dd>dream; fancy; daydream</dd><br>
<dd>일어날 가능성이 적은 헛되고 황당한 생각을 하다.</dd><br>
<dd>To have a useless, absurd thought that has little chance of happening.</dd><br>
</li>
</ul>